text: Aleksandra Artyomenko (14 January 1928 - 25 September 2010) was a Soviet alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1928 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Soviet female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Krasnoyarsk Krai
